When asked to create a React component:
- Use functional components with TypeScript.
- Fetch data using Supabase Client or SWR.
- Follow a clean and modular folder structure.
- Use TailwindCSS for styling if applicable.
- Ensure components are reusable and composable.
- Include loading and error states.
